OL,3,CRicky Hatton's son announces boxing
OL,4,Ccomeback
OL,6,FCampbell Hatton, the son of the late
OL,7,FRicky Hatton, has announced his return
OL,8,Fto boxing after retiring following his
OL,9,Fdad's death.
OL,11,FThe 25-year-old confirmed his comeback
OL,12,Fduring the Misfits boxing show in
OL,13,FManchester on Saturday, nearly two
OL,14,Fyears after his last fight.
OL,16,FDuring the broadcast for the Eddie
OL,17,FHall vs Tommy Fury fight, Campbell
OL,18,Fmade the announcement, telling the
OL,19,Fcrowd, "Its all about doing him
OL,20,F(Ricky) proud".
