OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781651952
OL,3,CRicky Hatton's son announces boxing
OL,4,Ccomeback
OL,6,FCampbell was also asked about
OL,7,Fpotential future opponents.
OL,9,FOn the rumours that he could go head
OL,10,Fto head with Aadam Hamed, the son of
OL,11,FPrince Naseem, he said: "I'd love it
OL,12,Fstraight away, makes sense two massive
OL,13,Fboxing names, big boxing families, so
OL,14,Fwhy not".
OL,16,FThroughout his short career Campbell
OL,17,Fhas amassed a 14-2 record.
OL,19,FHis father, Ricky was a two weight
OL,20,Fworld champion and one of the nations
OL,21,Fbest loved boxers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
