OL,3,CRicky Hatton's son announces boxing
OL,4,Ccomeback
OL,6,FHe died at the age of 46 in September
OL,7,F2025 before being found in his Hyde
OL,8,Fhome by his manager.
OL,10,FSpeaking to Granada Reports in
OL,11,FOctober, Campbell said his family had
OL,12,Fbeen "hit for six" and left
OL,13,F"heartbroken" following his fathers
OL,14,Fdeath.
OL,16,FCampbell is not the only Hatton who
OL,17,Fhas made headlines, Ricky's niece Lola
OL,18,FHatton made her England debut in the
OL,19,FFour Nations tournament in Scotland
OL,20,Fand won gold for the England Schools
OL,21,Fteam.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
